{"tid":1728160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成：民建聯支持成立獨立委員會調查警暴","createTime":"2019-11-16T17:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T22:03:56.000Z","uid":305531,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f89943674da22567f168c64722ee6d55a9155ea3","tid":1728160,"uid":305531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"Tsang: Even if she agrees to negotiate on real universal suffrage, it will still be very difficult to come to an agreement. It can&rsquo;t be done at once and satisfy everybody. The only demand that could be met is the commission of inquiry.<br />\n曾鈺成: 即使林鄭同意就真正的普選權進行談判，也很難達成協議。這不可能一次完成，每個人都會滿意。可以滿足的唯一需求是調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\nB&eacute;ja: If you declare publicly that it is necessary to set it up, it might help.<br />\n法國學者 B&eacute;ja: 如果您公開聲明有必要進行設置，則可能會有所幫助。<br />\n<br />\nTsang: Judge Andrew Li said it.<br />\n曾鈺成: 李國能法官已經講了。<br />\n<br />\nB&eacute;ja: But nobody from the DAB has.<br />\n法國學者 B&eacute;ja: 但是民建聯沒有人講過。<br />\n<br />\nTsang: Good point. However, the DAB won&rsquo;t go public with anything they know the government can&rsquo;t do. In private, they have been urging Carrie to establish it. But as long as she refuses, they won&rsquo;t say anything.<br />\n曾鈺成:  說得對。但是，民建聯不會公開任何他們知道政府做不到的事情。私下里，他們一直在敦促林鄭成立調查委員會。但是只要她拒絕，他們就什麼也不會說。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/11/16/interview-ex-head-legislature-jasper-tsang-says-govt-weakest-player-four-hong-kongs-struggle/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F11%2F16%2Finterview-ex-head-legislature-jasper-tsang-says-govt-weakest-player-four-hong-kongs-struggle%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz2Abrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=6a324ab9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/11/16/interview-ex-head-legislature-jasper-tsang-says-govt-weakest-player-four-hong-kongs-struggle/</a>"},{"pid":"4a3257a5103518e5c6d4ccc8cac87a2fb18f8575","tid":1728160,"uid":189157,"like":1